  
  Now it is time to learn how to run nuclei templates... 
    
    1. URL 1: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates
       URL 2: https://nuclei.projectdiscovery.io/nuclei/get-started/
       URL 3: https://nuclei.projectdiscovery.io/nuclei/get-started/#nuclei-config
    
       Example (CVE-2021-44228: Solr/Log4j2: RCE): 
    
        Step 1: Build up the vulnerable image (https://github.com/vulhub/vulhub/tree/master/log4j/CVE-2021-44228)
        
            The admin portal of Apache Solr will be seen at http://your-ip:8983

        Step 2: In another terminal start the scan for CVE-2021-44228 by using Nuclei
        
        $ sudo docker run -ti  projectdiscovery/nuclei -u https://192.168.137.192:8983 -t cves/2021/CVE-2021-44228.yaml  
         
        This command not works true,  It will be fixed .....


    
